        "content": "<html><head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><style type=\"text/css\" style=\"display:none\">\r\n<!--\r\np\r\n\t{margin-top:0;\r\n\tmargin-bottom:0}\r\n-->\r\n</style></head><body dir=\"ltr\"><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">Hi,</span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">We are writing in to request for CV under the GVT(T)24014 Agile Co-Development and ICT Professional Services Master Contract for Category 1A Services (Individuals Onshore).</span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>&nbsp;</b></span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>Project Requirements:</b></span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">We require the following Service Personnel for an upcoming project from the period of 01/11/2025 to 30/04/2027:</span></p><div style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><div class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin:0px; font-family:FluentSy