yle=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; border-right:1pt solid; border-bottom:1pt solid; padding-right:5.4pt; padding-left:5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:142.5pt\"><p class=\"skipProofing\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0)\">Consultant</span></p></td><td style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; border-right:1pt solid; border-bottom:1pt solid; padding-right:5.4pt; padding-left:5.4pt; vertical-align:top; width:84.7pt\"><p class=\"skipProofing\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0)\">1</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>&nbsp;</b></span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>Job Descriptions:</b></span></p><ol start=\"1\" style=\"text-align:left; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255)\"><li style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0); margin:0px\"><span role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size:11pt\">Attached is the job description for the role requirements of IT Infrastructure Engineer.</span></li><li style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0); margin:0px\"><span role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size:11pt\">Please refer to Part 2 Section A Annex 1 of the Master Contract for detailed job descriptions, responsibilities, and required qualifications for each role.</span></li></ol><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>&nbsp;</b></span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>Submission Requirements:</b></span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">Please provide the following for each proposed Service Personnel:</span></p><ul style=\"text-align:left; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255)\"><li style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0); margin:0px\"><span role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size:11pt\">Detailed curriculum vitae</span></li><li style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0); margin:0px\"><span role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size:11pt\">Job role and skill level classification</span></li><li style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0); margin:0px\"><span role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size:11pt\">Availability and start date</span></li><li style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0); margin:0px\"><span role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size:11pt\">Proposed pricing (as per Master Contract rates)</span></li><li style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:12pt; color:rgb(0,0,0); margin:0px\"><span role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size:11pt\">Any relevant certifications or qualifications</span></li></ul><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>&nbsp;</b></span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>Evaluation Process:</b></span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">Proposed candidates may be required to undergo technical assessments and interviews as part of our evaluation process.</span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>&nbsp;</b></span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>Please submit your response in softcopy format by 13/10/2025 (3 working days).</b></span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>&nbsp;</b></span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>Should you have any queries regarding this CV Request, please feel free to contact me.</b></span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif; font-size:11pt; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">Thank you for your participation.</span></p><p class=\"elementToProof\" style=\"text-align:left; text-indent:0px; background-co